Some features which would be nice to have in future releases:

- submenus in command and file popup menus

- tabbed dialog for all the stuff in the options menu

- tooltips on icon gadgets

- truncate very long filenames in the file and shelf views

- fix overflowing container views in large directories

- multicolumn list layout for configuring file type action lists

- dialogs for devices/shelf/command menu setup

- background copying and deletion

- builtin find operation

- support for png icons (announced for OpenMotif 2.3)

- support for virtual filesystems (ftp, tar, etc.)

- support for xdnd interoperability
